me in behind those who asked first.</p>\n<p>One of the ways a WordPress Plugin or Widget makes it into WordPress.com is by being among the top downloaded and most popular Plugins on the <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/\" title=\"WordPress Plugins Extends\">WordPress Plugin Directory</a>. If you have the full version of WordPress, have your say on how you like it, and encourage others to download and install it.</p>\n<p>I really think that the blog comment war is going to heat up with this new hot Plugin.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://lorelle.files.wordpress.com/2006/08/sig.gif\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<hr />\n<p><font size=\"-1\"><b>Site Search Tags:</b> <a href=\"http://lorelle.wordpress.com/index.php?s=liz+strauss\" rel=\"tag\">liz strauss</a>, <a href=\"http://lorelle.wordpress.com/index.php?s=liz+strauss+comment+counter+wordpress+plugin\" rel=\"tag\">liz strauss comment counter wordpress plugin</a>, <a href=\"http://lorelle.wordpress.com/index.php?s=wordpress+plugin\" rel=\"tag\">wordpress plugin</a>, <a href=\"http://lorelle.wordpress.com/index.php?s=comment+count\" rel=\"tag\">comment count</a>, <a href=\"http://lorelle.wordpress.com/index.php?s=comment+counter\" rel=\"tag\">comment counter</a>, <a href=\"http://lorelle.wordpress.com/index.php?s=ozh\" rel=\"tag\">ozh</a>, <a href=\"http://lorelle.wordpress.com/index.php?s=planetozh\" rel=\"tag\">planetozh</a>, <a href=\"http://lorelle.wordpress.com/index.php?s=count+your+comments\" rel=\"tag\">count your comments</a>, <a href=\"http://lorelle.wordpress.com/index.php?s=blog+comments\" rel=\"tag\">blog comments</a>, <a href=\"http://lorelle.wordpress.com/index.php?s=blog+conversation\" rel=\"tag\">blog conversation</a>, <a href=\"http://lorelle.wordpress.com/index.php?s=comment+score\" rel=\"tag\">comment score</a>, <a href=\"http://lorelle.wordpress.com/index.php?s=comment+score+card\" rel=\"tag\">comment score card</a>, <a href=\"http://lorelle.wordpress.com/index.php?s=wordpress+tips\" rel=\"tag\">wordp